data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Lovely 3/2/2home with upgrade touches throughout. Replaced roof and added gutters in 2019, New HVAC in April 2022,  new HWH & mailbox. As you enter the screened front entry notice the new decorative tile flooring. Step through the front door and see the open vaulted ceiling into the living and dining area. To the left are the master bedroom with crown molding, ensuite bath with double sinks and shower, and large walk in closet. Two more guest bedrooms share a full bath with updated tile. All updated flooring except one of the guest rooms. The updated kitchen  includes a breakfast nook with stand alone buffet. Outside is a covered patio with a screened in swimming pool surrounded by fenced in yard with shed. Roll down blinds in the pool area convey.
